---
/**
 * Global CTA section — "Build your product roadmap"
 * Used as a pre-footer CTA across all pages.
 * Single source of truth for copy, styling, and structure.
 */
---

<div class="predictability-cta">
  <div class="predictability-cta-inner">
    <div class="predictability-cta-content">
      <span class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--accent);">Start Here</span>
      <h2>Build your product roadmap in under 60 seconds.</h2>
      <p>Describe your product idea in plain language. NolteOS analyzes it against 20 years of experience and historic delivery data and surfaces:</p>
      <ul class="cta-checklist">
        <li>Competitive landscape — where you can differentiate and win</li>
        <li>Risk areas — regulatory, technical, and market challenges</li>
        <li>Growth opportunities — where to evolve after launch</li>
        <li>Delivery forecast — scope, timeline, and cost to get there</li>
      </ul>
      <a class="btn-accent" href="https://os.nolte.io">Build Your Product Roadmap &rarr;</a>
      <span class="cta-micro">Free assessment. No sales call required. <a href="/contact" style="color: var(--accent); text-decoration: underline;">Or just talk to us.</a></span>
    </div>
    <div class="predictability-cta-visual">
      <div class="os-preview">
        <div class="os-section-label">Product Opportunity Assessment</div>
        <div class="os-roadmap">
          <div class="os-roadmap-header">
            <div class="os-roadmap-col">Area</div>
            <div class="os-roadmap-months">
              <span>Risk</span><span>Opportunity</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="os-roadmap-row">
            <div class="os-roadmap-label">Regulatory<div class="os-roadmap-meta">HIPAA · State filing</div></div>
            <div class="os-roadmap-track">
              <div class="os-roadmap-bar os-bar-strategy" style="width:35%;left:0"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="os-roadmap-row">
            <div class="os-roadmap-label">Market Fit<div class="os-roadmap-meta">Competitive positioning</div></div>
            <div class="os-roadmap-track">
              <div class="os-roadmap-bar os-bar-build" style="width:55%;left:30%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="os-roadmap-row">
            <div class="os-roadmap-label">Growth<div class="os-roadmap-meta">Post-launch evolution</div></div>
            <div class="os-roadmap-track">
              <div class="os-roadmap-bar os-bar-launch" style="width:45%;left:55%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="os-roadmap-summary">
          <span>3 risk areas</span>
          <span>5 opportunities</span>
          <span>Let's talk</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
